flowchart TD
    A[UDAM failure cases] --> B[No information]
    A --> C[High cost]
    A --> D[Misleading feedback]
    A --> E[Compulsive checking]
    A --> F[Non-diffusing state]
    A --> G[Safety-critical delay]
    A --> H[Wrong anchor]

    B --> B1["I(a)=0 and B(a)=0"]
    C --> C1["C(a) > I(a)+B(a)"]
    D --> D1[False confidence or biased update]
    E --> E1[Marginal I(a) approaches 0]
    F --> F1["Q=0"]
    G --> G1[Measurement delays necessary action]
    H --> H1[Action measures irrelevant variable]

    B:::bad
    C:::bad
    D:::bad
    E:::bad
    F:::warn
    G:::bad
    H:::bad

    classDef bad fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef warn fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00,stroke-width:1px;
